@page "/variantes"
@layout VariantCLayout

<PageTitle>Propuestas de Diseño | San Pablo Vet Clínic</PageTitle>

<section class="vs-page">
    <div class="vs-header">
        <span class="vs-label">Propuestas de Diseño</span>
        <h1>6 propuestas, 1 decisión</h1>
        <p>Cada variante tiene la misma identidad visual pero una estructura diferente. Haz clic en la que prefieras para verla en pantalla completa.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-grid">
        <!-- A -->
        <NavLink href="home-a" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--a">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--light">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-bar"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-cta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge vs-badge--teal">A</span>
                <h2>Hospital Elegante</h2>
                <p>Minimalista y sofisticado. Mucho espacio blanco, estética de clínica premium que transmite <strong>confianza y seriedad</strong>.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Hero con foto de fachada y overlay suave</li>
                    <li>Barra de acceso rápido a urgencias</li>
                    <li>Servicios con imágenes reales</li>
                    <li>Especialistas y Vet Móvil destacados</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>

        <!-- C -->
        <NavLink href="home-c" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--c">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav vs-mock-nav--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--dark">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn vs-mock-btn--coral"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-dots"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-bar"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-cta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge vs-badge--white">C</span>
                <h2>Moderno Carousel</h2>
                <p>Hero oscuro con <strong>carousel de 3 slides</strong>, barra de acceso rápido, servicios con imágenes y secciones blancas limpias.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Carousel hero interactivo con 3 slides</li>
                    <li>Quick bar con urgencias destacada</li>
                    <li>Grid 3×2 de servicios con fotos</li>
                    <li>Especialistas verticales + Vet Móvil</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>

        <!-- C3 -->
        <NavLink href="home-c3" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--c3">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav vs-mock-nav--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--dark">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn vs-mock-btn--coral"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section vs-mock-section--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section vs-mock-section--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section vs-mock-section--dark"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge vs-badge--coral">C3</span>
                <h2>One-Page Flow</h2>
                <p>Todo accesible sin salir de la página. Scroll fluido con secciones completas inline y <strong>mínima navegación externa</strong>.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Toda la info clave en una sola página</li>
                    <li>Secciones alternas dark/light fluidas</li>
                    <li>Especialistas con bio detallada inline</li>
                    <li>Contacto completo integrado</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-divider">
        <span>Variantes híbridas</span>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-grid">
        <!-- D -->
        <NavLink href="home-d" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--d">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav vs-mock-nav--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--dark">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn vs-mock-btn--coral"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-dots"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-bar" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-alert"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-cta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge vs-badge--teal">D</span>
                <h2>Carousel + Info Completa</h2>
                <p>Lo mejor de C y C3: <strong>carousel hero interactivo</strong> + contenido detallado inline. Todo sobre fondos blancos.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Carousel hero de 3 slides</li>
                    <li>Urgencias inline con teléfono y dirección</li>
                    <li>Especialistas horizontales con bio detallada</li>
                    <li>Servicios con imagen + contacto completo</li>
                    <li>Explore chips para páginas secundarias</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>

        <!-- E -->
        <NavLink href="home-e" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--e">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav vs-mock-nav--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--dark vs-mock-hero--editorial">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short vs-mock-line--white" style="margin-top:auto"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long vs-mock-line--white"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn vs-mock-btn--coral"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-strip-coral"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--wide"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row" style="direction:rtl">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--wide"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section vs-mock-section--dark"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-cta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge vs-badge--coral">E</span>
                <h2>Editorial Visual</h2>
                <p>Layout tipo revista. Servicios con <strong>imágenes grandes</strong> asimétricos, hero cinematográfico y sección about full-width.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Hero cinematográfico (texto abajo-izquierda)</li>
                    <li>Urgencia strip coral slim e impactante</li>
                    <li>Servicios como feature cards asimétricos</li>
                    <li>About full-width con imagen de fondo</li>
                    <li>Especialistas con badges de color</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-divider">
        <span>Diseño anterior</span>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-grid">
        <!-- Old -->
        <NavLink href="home-old" class="vs-card">
            <div class="vs-card__preview vs-card__preview--old">
                <div class="vs-mock-nav"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-hero vs-mock-hero--light">
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--short"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-line vs-mock-line--long"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-btn"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-bar"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-row">
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                    <div class="vs-mock-card vs-mock-card--img"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="vs-mock-section"></div>
                <div class="vs-mock-cta"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-card__body">
                <span class="vs-badge" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">OLD</span>
                <h2>Diseño Original</h2>
                <p>El home original basado en <strong>componentes modulares</strong>. Hero con foto, carousel de anuncios, servicios y testimonios.</p>
                <ul class="vs-traits">
                    <li>Hero profesional con foto y overlay</li>
                    <li>Carousel de anuncios interactivo</li>
                    <li>Feature cards y servicios en grid</li>
                    <li>Sección "¿Por qué elegirnos?"</li>
                    <li>Testimonios de clientes</li>
                </ul>
                <span class="vs-go">Ver variante →</span>
            </div>
        </NavLink>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-footer">
        <p>💡 Cada variante comparte la misma paleta de colores e identidad. La diferencia es la <strong>estructura</strong> y el <strong>estilo visual</strong>.</p>
        <NavLink href="" class="vs-back">← Volver al inicio</NavLink>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .vs-page { min-height: 100vh; padding: 2rem; background: #0d0d0d; }

    .vs-header { text-align: center; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; }
    .vs-label { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-coral); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .vs-header h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-h1); color: white; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
    .vs-header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.7; }

    .vs-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.75rem; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .vs-card {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
        background: #161616; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden;
        text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .vs-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); border-color: rgba(98,171,191,0.3); }

    .vs-card__preview {
        padding: 1.25rem; background: #111; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;
        border-radius: 8px; margin: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Mock elements */
    .vs-mock-nav { height: 6%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-nav--dark { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .vs-mock-hero--light { height: 28%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4f7, #f0f4f8); border-radius: 3px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 8% 10%; gap: 4px; }
    .vs-mock-hero--dark { height: 30%; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e); border-radius: 3px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 8% 10%; gap: 4px; }
    .vs-mock-hero--editorial { justify-content: flex-end; }
    .vs-mock-line { height: 5px; border-radius: 3px; background: #ddd; }
    .vs-mock-line--short { width: 40%; }
    .vs-mock-line--long { width: 70%; }
    .vs-mock-line--white { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
    .vs-mock-btn { width: 28%; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--primary-teal); margin-top: 2px; }
    .vs-mock-btn--coral { background: var(--accent-coral); }
    .vs-mock-dots { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .vs-mock-dots::before, .vs-mock-dots::after { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
    .vs-mock-dots::before { background: white; width: 16px; border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-bar { height: 10px; background: rgba(98,171,191,0.08); border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-alert { height: 8px; background: rgba(187,84,95,0.25); border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-strip-coral { height: 6px; background: rgba(187,84,95,0.4); border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-row { display: flex; gap: 4px; flex: 0 0 auto; }
    .vs-mock-card { flex: 1; height: 40px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 4px; }
    .vs-mock-card--img { height: 45px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(98,171,191,0.12) 55%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 55%); }
    .vs-mock-card--wide { flex: 1.3; }
    .vs-mock-section { height: 18px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 3px; }
    .vs-mock-section--dark { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .vs-mock-cta { height: 12px; background: rgba(187,84,95,0.15); border-radius: 3px; margin-top: auto; }

    /* Card body */
    .vs-card__body { padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: var(--font-size-sm); font-weight: 700; width: fit-content; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .vs-badge--coral { background: rgba(187,84,95,0.15); color: var(--accent-coral); }
    .vs-badge--teal { background: rgba(98,171,191,0.15); color: var(--primary-teal); }
    .vs-badge--white { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; }
    .vs-card__body h2 { font-size: 1.375rem; color: white; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .vs-card__body p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.6; font-size: var(--font-size-sm); margin: 0 0 0.75rem; }
    .vs-card__body strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
    .vs-traits { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .vs-traits li { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); padding-left: 1rem; position: relative; }
    .vs-traits li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--primary-teal); font-weight: 700; }
    .vs-go { color: var(--primary-teal); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--font-size-sm); margin-top: auto; }

    /* Divider */
    .vs-divider {
        text-align: center; margin: 3rem auto 2rem; max-width: 1000px;
        position: relative;
    }
    .vs-divider::before {
        content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 0; right: 0;
        height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .vs-divider span {
        position: relative; background: #0d0d0d; padding: 0 1.5rem;
        font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--primary-teal);
        font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .vs-footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .vs-footer p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); }
    .vs-footer strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .vs-back { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--primary-teal); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--font-size-sm); }
    .vs-back:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .vs-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .vs-card__preview { max-height: 200px; margin: 0.5rem; }
    }
</style>
